<div id="page" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<div dir="ltr" id="content" lang="en"><span class="anchor" id="top"></span>
<span class="anchor" id="line-6"></span><p class="line862">A category is a <a href="/WikiName">WikiName</a> that exploits <a class="interwiki" href="http://c2.com/cgi/wiki?WikiWiki" title="Wiki">WikiWiki</a>'s reverse linking: if you click on the title of a category page, you'll get a list of pages belonging to that category. To get a list of all categories, click the Category<strong></strong>Category title in the navigation area. <span class="anchor" id="line-7"></span><span class="anchor" id="line-8"></span><p class="line874">Additionally, you can add lists of all pages which are members of that particular category to the category page using macros like this: <span class="anchor" id="line-9"></span><span class="anchor" id="line-10"></span><p class="line862">Here is a list of all pages containing the CategoryCategory wiki tag: <span class="anchor" id="line-11"></span><div class="searchresults">
<ol start="1"><li><a href="/CategoryHomepage?highlight=%28%5CbCategoryCategory%5Cb%29">CategoryHomepage</a></li><li><a href="/CategoryMergeAlgorithm?highlight=%28%5CbCategoryCategory%5Cb%29">CategoryMergeAlgorithm</a></li><li><a href="/CategoryMergeExample?highlight=%28%5CbCategoryCategory%5Cb%29">CategoryMergeExample</a></li><li><a href="/CategoryTemplate?highlight=%28%5CbCategoryCategory%5Cb%29">CategoryTemplate</a></li><li><a href="/Crusher%2BJaw%2BCrusher%2Bvipeak?highlight=%28%5CbCategoryCategory%5Cb%29">Crusher+Jaw+Crusher+vipeak</a></li><li><a href="/GetText%28Edit%29?highlight=%28%5CbCategoryCategory%5Cb%29">GetText(Edit)</a></li><li><a href="/ScalarMerge?highlight=%28%5CbCategoryCategory%5Cb%29">ScalarMerge</a></li><li><a href="/grinding_mill_manufacturer_vipeak?highlight=%28%5CbCategoryCategory%5Cb%29">grinding_mill_manufacturer_vipeak</a></li><li><a href="/grinding_mill_roller_mill_manufacturer_vipeak?highlight=%28%5CbCategoryCategory%5Cb%29">grinding_mill_roller_mill_manufacturer_vipeak</a></li><li><a href="/mining_machinery_manufacturer_vipeak?highlight=%28%5CbCategoryCategory%5Cb%29">mining_machinery_manufacturer_vipeak</a></li><li><a href="/stone_crusher_vipeak?highlight=%28%5CbCategoryCategory%5Cb%29">stone_crusher_vipeak</a></li></ol>
</div> <span class="anchor" id="line-12"></span><span class="anchor" id="line-13"></span><p class="line862">To be consistent with the C2 category scheme, all categories start with the word "Category". For more information, see <a class="interwiki" href="http://c2.com/cgi/wiki?AboutCategoriesAndTopics" title="Wiki">AboutCategoriesAndTopics</a><strong></strong>. <span class="anchor" id="line-14"></span><span class="anchor" id="bottom"></span></div>
